<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[٩]</span> ثُمَّ عَمَّةٌ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١٠]</span> ثُمَّ بِنْتُ أَخٍ وَأُخْتٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[١١]</span> ثُمَّ بِنْتُ عَمٍّ وَعَمَّةٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[١٢]</span> ثُمَّ بِنْتُ عَمِّ أَبٍ وَعَمَّتِهِ <span class="c2">(١)</span> عَلَى مَا فُصِّلَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[١٣]</span> ثُمَّ لِبَاقِي العَصَبَةِ الأَقْرَبِ فَالأَقْرَبِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَشُرِطَ كَوْنُهُ مَحْرَماً لِأُنْثَى.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[١٤]</span> ثُمَّ لِذِي رَحِمٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[١٥]</span> ثُمَّ لِحَاكِمٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَلَا تَثْبُتُ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- لِمَنْ فِيهِ رِقٌّ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَلَا لِكَافِرٍ عَلَى مُسْلِمٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- وَلَا لِفَاسِقٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- وَلَا لِمُزَوَّجَةٍ بِأَجْنَبِيٍّ مِنْ مَحْضُونٍ مِنْ حِينِ عَقْدٍ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنْ أَرَادَ أَحَدُ أَبَوَيْهِ نُقْلَةً إِلَى بَلَدٍ آمِنٍ:</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>- وَطَرِيقُهُ مَسَافَةُ قَصْرٍ فَأَكْثَرُ،<span class="c5"> لِيَسْكُنَهُ:</span> فَأَبٌ أَحَقُّ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) في (د): ثم أب وعمته. مكان قوله: (وعمته).</p> </div>